Class GroundAtom

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umd.cs.psl.model.atom.Atom
      • edu.umd.cs.psl.model.atom.GroundAtom
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Formula
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ObservedAtom, RandomVariableAtom

    public abstract class GroundAtom
extends Atom
    An Atom with only GroundTerms for arguments.

    A GroundAtom has a truth value and a confidence value.
